{"tid":1944501,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【眾籌】【鄭文傑團隊】召集香港人支援英國抗疫 #HKSTANDSWITHHK","createTime":"2020-03-26T12:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T08:49:44.000Z","uid":137109,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"a56a5da3f31c6fb02966e4c9c6a3ca5fee5d268e","tid":1944501,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T12:13:01.000Z","msg":"Link: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/XS87yCJO7HA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXS87yCJO7HA&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=f1636aac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XS87yCJO7HA</a><br />\n<br />\n英國家陣比武肺搞到一鑊泡，國會停擺，王儲中招，幾嚴重唔駛我多講！成個社會、醫療系統幾乎比肺炎拖垮；尤其NHS頂住極大人力、資源上壓力。<br />\n我哋組織The Umbrella Union由Simon Cheng  鄭文傑 牽頭，希望可以藉此喚起關注，響應英國呼籲，喺英國國家危急關頭支援NHS醫護對抗呢場全球大流行嘅疫情。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">英國NHS關香港人咩事？ </div><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔少為香港問題發聲嘅政客／議員，好似Benedict Rogers 同Luke de Pulford都公開呼籲為NHS提供協助， 而曾經係上議院插爆緊急法嘅Baroness Northover，自己亦中咗招。連一向同中共威權政體唔啱掗既查理斯王子都中埋。 <br />\n我哋亦需要NHS維持在英手足嘅健康，人無事先可以繼續抗爭，繼續國際戰線上努力。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家仲記唔記得，台灣捐款救助日本震災？日本下至民眾上至政界，一心支持台灣，係我哋向英國搞好民間交往嘅絕佳範例！最緊要係，今次香港 Stand with the UK，以後叫英國Stand with Hong Kong就容易好多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nKong U 醫學院前身 香港華人西醫書院 除咗出咗孫中山之外，仲為香港醫療打咗好基礎。而今日香港有世界級嘅醫療體系，英國絕對功不可沒（當然我哋嘅醫護都係啦）。係呢個重要時刻我哋幫返英國轉頭，支持NHS度過難關 ，令英國人知道香港人係幫得手，亦都令佢地之後幫返我地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗關注情況/Share開去，有餘力可以考慮課金，捐款將會直接交俾NHS，支援當地前線醫護。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">我哋係邊個？ </div><br />\n我哋係一班在英香港人，來自不同界別(醫療、公務員、學術、藝術、金融），由 Simon Cheng 鄭文傑 牽頭，參與光復香港嘅國際戰線。<br />\n#HKStandswithUK"},{"pid":"1df0ec77925d9b4b2af1b67f2bcaa7fbdae753bc","tid":1944501,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T12:14:43.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"e4949dfba01bb9475778913013e1c3dde1a103b7","tid":1944501,"uid":199580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T12:15:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a0555214854be81e9e3e67e8d0be34fc3ae13f18","tid":1944501,"uid":199580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T12:15:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e45bbebb459ace5d6250b0dff721c7af76d75586","tid":1944501,"uid":199580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T12:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a8086a85bbc6bf11745c580367a4a3fc1f58a5","tid":1944501,"uid":199580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T12:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b63da528c0ddbec15d1d7a29ca3e7ce1430bbb5","tid":1944501,"uid":196020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T12:16:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2e3eae5c116e63f77bc2d52f96d57662858f99eb","tid":1944501,"uid":199580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T12:16:12.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ee7a2165a75b9ca2a67bd4bfeb1c9c70adbc12bf","tid":1944501,"uid":199580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T12:16:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3a65c1973bf7d5